From 14c77caaacdefbc8b1d887e863917132607295d2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Christian Hewitt <christianshewitt@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Mar 2026 05:30:02 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 13/39] WIP: media: platform: amlogic: add meson-demux driver

The meson-demux driver handles demux of signals from demod/tuner
chips and supports dvb-frontend operations. The driver has been
adapted from the Amlogic Linux 5.15 vendor kernel.

Signed-off-by: Christian Hewitt <christianshewitt@gmail.com>
